edu.neu.coe.info6205.life.base

Class Grid

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.neu.coe.info6205.life.base.Grid
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Countable, Renderable

    public class Grid
extends java.lang.Object
implements Countable, Renderable
    This class represents an infinite grid on which the game of life can be played. There can be independent groups in the grid, but if they ever overlap, they must be merged. In practice, you will typically only have one group in a grid.
